# Paste your Azure Application (client) ID on the line below, then copy this file to
# microsoft-client-id (same folder). That file is gitignored — only your builds use it.
#
# Azure redirect URI (register once): industrialislauncher://oauth/microsoft
#
# Or set MICROSOFT_CLIENT_ID when building:
#   $env:MICROSOFT_CLIENT_ID="your-client-id"; cargo tauri build
#
# Example:
# 2c053cfe-b7a6-4bec-bed5-5e1bb33ca797